‚úàÔ∏è AI Travel Planner: Dream Trip Generator

Project Overview

The AI Travel Planner is a modern web application designed to simplify and personalize the process of planning complex trips. Instead of manually searching for destinations, activities, and estimating costs, users simply input their travel parameters (dates, starting point, destination, and interests), and the application uses the Gemini API to generate a detailed, day-by-day itinerary complete with an estimated budget.

This tool aims to provide a reliable starting point for travel planning, blending the creativity of a large language model with structured, actionable travel data.

‚ú® Key Features

Intelligent Itinerary Generation: Leverage the Gemini API to create unique, optimized, and context-aware travel plans based on user input, focusing on declared interests.

Core Trip Customization: Input essential travel parameters:

Start Date

End Date

Starting Location

Final Destination

Interests/Themes: Specify activities like shopping, hiking, historical tours, local events, or culinary experiences.

Cost Estimation (Aspiration Feature): The AI attempts to provide a realistic, estimated budget for the suggested activities, accommodations, and transport. Note: Actual costs may vary.

User-Friendly Interface: A clean, responsive design ensures a seamless experience on both desktop and mobile devices.

üöÄ How to Use

Getting your personalized travel plan is quick and easy!

Access the Application: Open the web app in your browser.

Define Your Trip: Fill out the required fields in the input form:

Select your desired Start Date and End Date.

Enter your Starting Location (e.g., "San Francisco, CA").

Enter your Final Destination (e.g., "Tokyo, Japan").

Specify your Interests/Themes (e.g., "Shopping and Fine Dining," "Hiking and Nature Trails," "Historical Sites") to guide the itinerary suggestions.

Generate Plan: Click the "Generate Travel Plan" button.

Review & Refine: The AI will process the request and display a structured itinerary, including suggested activities, transportation, and the estimated cost breakdown.

üåü Future Enhancements

Accommodation/Flight Search Integration: Add options to directly search or link to booking sites for suggested itinerary items.

Multi-Modal Itineraries: Integrate image generation to visualize key destinations.

Detailed Cost Breakdowns: Improve the accuracy of cost estimations by allowing users to specify travel class (Economy/Business), preferred accommodation style (Hostel/Hotel), etc.
